# Hello World

Welcome to your new blog powered by **TinaCMS**!

TinaCMS is a Git-backed headless CMS with visual editing capabilities. Your content is stored as Markdown files directly in your repository.

## Getting Started

1. Edit this post by navigating to `/admin` in your browser
2. Create new posts through the TinaCMS admin interface
3. Content changes are saved as commits to your repository

## Features

- **Visual Editing**: Edit content directly on your pages
- **Git-Backed**: All content is stored in your repository
- **Markdown**: Content is stored as Markdown files
- **Type-Safe**: Auto-generated TypeScript types for your content

Happy writing!
